E '''Deliya Grigore''' si ekh [[Romni]] andar e [[Rumuniya]] (biyandili: 7 Februara 1972, kay [[Galats]]). Voi barili kana e Rumuniya sas xulayardi e komunisturendar thay e Roma nas ekh prinjardi [[sel]] (laki familiya garvdyas lengo caco sel). Palal [[1990]]to bershesko, kana e komunisturya peravden pen, voi dashti te phenel ke si caci Romni thay te palemsiklyovel e [[Romani chib]] <ref>http://www.bbc.co.uk/romanian/news/story/2005/07/050708_romi_cultura.shtml Lake vakyarimata kay BBC (Rumunikanes)</ref>. Deatuncara, voi keres buti po Romano sanskrtipe thay arakhel e Romane cacimata. [[2002]]to bershesko, manglyas e Rumuniyako statesko thay e xulaipnastar e [[Rumunikani Ortodoksi Kristiyani Khangeri|Rumunikane Ortodokse Kristiyane Khangeryako]] te prinjarel e bilachimata so kerdyas panj [[shelbersh]]a, ando vaxt e [[Romengi robiya andi valaxiya thay Moldova|robiyako sistemo]], ama von ci phenden palpale khanc <ref>http://www.evenimentul.ro/articol/rromii-solicita-autoritatilor-si.html Lekh kay ''Evenimentul'' (Rumunikanes)</ref>.

